OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FThere will be some sunshine on
OL,6,FMonday, though it will gradually turn
OL,7,Fcloudier from the east. A slight
OL,8,Feasterly breeze developing, though
OL,9,Ffeeling pleasant enough in any
OL,10,Flingering brighter breaks.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,13,FTuesday looks cloudier with the odd
OL,14,Fshower. A chance of a shower on
OL,15,FWednesday and Thursday, though some
OL,16,Fsunshine too. A strong and gusty wind
OL,17,Fdeveloping for a time.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
